HEADWORD: Bard
<hw>Bard</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <fld>(Cookery)</fld> <def>To cover (meat
or game) with a thin slice of fat bacon.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

